snippet.title: iPhone/iPad/Mac RESIDENT EVIL 7 biohazard Pre-Order Trailer
snippet.description:
Resident Evil 7 biohazard is out now for iPhone 15 Pro models and all iPad and Mac with M-series chips! A special discount is also available to celebrate launch! 

More info here: bit.ly/REIOS
